<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Detail API Key</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* Navbar Styling (Sama dengan Dashboard) */
    .navbar {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      height: 70px;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333 !important;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .btn-logout {
      background-color: #ff7675;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 8px 24px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-logout:hover {
      background-color: #d63031;
      color: white;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(214, 48, 49, 0.3);
    }

    /* Layout Spacing */
    .main-container {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    /* General Card Styling */
    .custom-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      background: white;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-header-main {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
      color: white;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-header-danger {
      background: #ff7675;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Detail List Styling */
    .detail-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #636e72;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .detail-value {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2d3436;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .detail-row {
      padding: 1rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    /* API Key Box */
    .apikey-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
      color: #e84393; /* Warna pinkish untuk code */
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* Status Badges */
    .status-badge {
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .status-valid { background-color: #e3f9e5; color: #27ae60; }
    .status-invalid { background-color: #ffeaea; color: #e15f41; }

    /* Action Buttons */
    .btn-delete {
      background-color: #d63031;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      width: 100%;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-delete:hover {
      background-color: #b71540;
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-back {
      background-color: #dfe6e9;
      color: #2d3436;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-back:hover {
      background-color: #b2bec3;
      color: #2d3436;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
        üöÄ Admin Dashboard
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/logout" class="btn btn-logout">
        Logout
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div style="height: 90px;"></div>

  <div class="container main-container">
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="card custom-card">
          <div class="card-header-main">
            <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">üìã Detail User & API Key</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            
            <div class="row detail-row">
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                <div class="detail-label">First Name</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= detail.first_name %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="detail-label">Last Name</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= detail.last_name %></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row detail-row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <div class="detail-label">Email Address</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= detail.email %></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row detail-row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <div class="detail-label">API Key</div>
                <div class="apikey-box">
                  <%= detail.api_key %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row detail-row">
              <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                <div class="detail-label">Status</div>
                <div class="mt-1">
                  <% if (detail.status === 'valid') { %>
                    <span class="status-badge status-valid">Valid</span>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <span class="status-badge status-invalid">Invalid</span>
                  <% } %>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                <div class="detail-label">Start Date</div>
                <div class="detail-value">
                  <%= new Date(detail.start_date).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="detail-label">End Date</div>
                <div class="detail-value">
                  <%= new Date(detail.end_date).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        
        <div class="card custom-card">
          <div class="card-header-danger">
            <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">‚ö†Ô∏è Perhatian</h6>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">
              Menghapus API Key ini bersifat permanen dan tidak dapat dibatalkan. User harus membuat key baru jika ini dihapus.
            </p>
            
            <form action="/admin/delete/<%= detail.id %>" method="POST" onsubmit="return confirm('Yakin ingin menghapus data ini secara permanen?');">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-delete shadow-sm">
                üóëÔ∏è Hapus API Key
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn btn-back">
          &larr; Kembali ke Dashboard
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>